    <content contentuid="h5e36bacegbf70g4e49g9681gf8e102b44698" version="1">Intricate mechanisms mesh with an enchanted bow-arm. The more seasoned its wielder becomes, the keener the weapon grows.</content>
    <content contentuid="h64a448f8ge2b3g452fg91fdg22458f7e6087" version="1">Growing Mechanism</content>
    <content contentuid="h74b2d28fg3b8cg49cbg8905g2bf34097bdd4" version="1">The enchantment increases with the wielder's level: +1 at level 4, +2 at level 7, and +3 at level 10. The first hit each turn deals additional Piercing damage equal to the wielder's level.</content>
    <content contentuid="h4c2a32d5gea2bg4065ga54eg71cb99cfa7ea" version="1">Mechanical Volley</content>
    <content contentuid="h9077a634g531bg4ccfgbf78g8457a91c6114" version="1">Spend a Bonus Action to make a normal shot with the Zhuge Repeating Crossbow. Once per turn.</content>
    <content contentuid="h6fb833c7g00d6g4d4fg946bgca266f7053ac" version="1">Kill-Chain Mechanism</content>
    <content contentuid="h94c0a64fg2ea1g41e3g9cc1g516950257061" version="1">When a shot from this weapon kills a hostile character, gain 1 Follow-Up stack. Each stack grants one free normal shot, which can trigger this effect again.</content>
    <content contentuid="hd11ec916g32d8g401cga19ag7a4bb69e8bfd" version="1">Follow-Up Shot</content>
    <content contentuid="hf409ba61g8fc6g4d74g9f46g6ea1cacdc3fe" version="1">Consume 1 Follow-Up stack to make a free normal shot with the Zhuge Repeating Crossbow.</content>
    <content contentuid="h08bcbc4fgdd04g4317g9b89g78eef2c8955a" version="1">Follow-Up Ready</content>
    <content contentuid="hab56ba2eg02e4g4611gb0e6gf43820362f5e" version="1">Each stack grants one free Follow-Up Shot. All stacks are cleared when combat ends, the wielder is incapacitated, or the crossbow is unequipped.</content>
